


'''Antiokecho Sant Theodosius''' zolmolo Mogarissos hea xarant, St. Basilachea prantant. Tacho bapui ‘Proherius’ ani tachi avoi ‘Eulogia’ dogaim` khub dhormvont aslim`. Khub vorsamni` tachi avoi ‘Eulogia’ ek Madr koxi vavrun, apleach putak ‘Theok’ atmik guru koso somzunk lagli. Jen'na to lhan also ten'na taka Abrahamachea pavlamni` cholpachi itsa yetali. Aple maink ani paik, ixtta-mitrank, ghorcheank ani sogllea sonvsari vostu soddun diunk to toyar also fokot Devachea moga khatir.

== Theodosiusachi Yatra ==

To aple viyajicher gelo ani Jeruzalem xaran pavlo. Jen'na to Antiokek pavlo, to Stylitachea ‘Sant Symeonak’ pollovpak ani tachi besanvam ani magnnim` magunk gelo. ‘Sant Symeonachea khambeaxim pavtokuch taka nanvam` milagricho yevkar dilo. To tea khambear choddlo ani tea Santa mukhar xaxttangi poddlo. ‘Symeonan taka mogachi veng marli ani tacher besanv ghatlem.

